snippet.title: Modern Japan by Kaminogi | Content Creator Pack | Cities: Skylines
snippet.description:
🌸Available on the 26th of March on all platforms! €4.99/$4.99🌸

Content Creator Pack: Modern Japan introduces a unique flair inspired by Japanese architecture with 20 unique, ploppable, buildings and six props from modder Ryuichi Kaminogi. Bring ornate models ranging from impressive skyscrapers to cozy udon and ramen shops to your city!

"そして日本のプレイヤーの皆様！　今回のCCPに含まれる建物たちは、私たち日本人にとって非常に馴染み深く、また便利で画期的なものになるはずです。このような素晴らしい機会をくれたParadox Interactiveの皆様、そしてここまで私を支援してくださった皆様に、深い感謝を捧げます！　Have fun!" - Kaminogi

"This CCP is definitely a milestone for me. I hope more people will become interested in Japan through this work. Thank you Paradox Interactive for this great opportunity! I'd also like to thank the players and creators who have supported me!" - Kaminogi

Check out the Store page and add it to your wishlist now!
https://pdxint.at/ModernJapan

Subscribe to Kaminogi on Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/RyuichiKaminogi
Follow and check him out on Steam: https://pdxint.at/KaminogiWS

----------------------------------------------------------------------
